Sonia Darrin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sonia_Darrin 0 Sonia Darrin (born Sonia Paskowitz; June 16, 1924) is a retired American film actress, best known as "Agnes Lowzier" in The Big Sleep (1946).
